  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK321">
<l>aṟaviṉai yāteṉiṟ kollāmai kōṟal</l>
<l>piṟaviṉai yellān tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Never to destroy life is the sum of all virtuous conduct. The destruction of life leads to every evil.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
